# Real Estate API

A RESTful API for managing real estate properties, listings, transactions, and user authentication built with Django REST Framework.

---

# Features

- User Registration
- User Sign In
- JWT Authentication
- User Logout with Token Blacklisting
- Property Management
- Listings Management
- Transactions Management
- CRUD Operations

---

# Technologies Used

- Python
- Django
- Django REST Framework
- Simple JWT
- drf-spectacular
- SQLite

---

# Project Applications

- users
- properties
- listings
- transactions

---

# Installation

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/boluwatife1110/Backend-Capstone.git
```

```bash
python -m venv myenv
```

---

## Activate Virtual Environment

### Windows

```bash
myenv\Scripts\activate
```

### Mac/Linux

```bash
source myenv/bin/activate
```

---

## Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

# Database Migration

```bash
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
```

---

# Run Server

```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

Server URL:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
```

---

# Authentication

This API uses JWT Authentication.

---

# Register User

## Endpoint

```http
POST /users/register/
```

## Request Body

```json
{
  "email": "user@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

---

# Sign In

## Endpoint

```http
POST /users/signin/
```

## Request Body

```json
{
  "email": "user@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "message": "Signin successful",
  "access_token": "your_access_token",
  "refresh_token": "your_refresh_token"
}
```

---

# Logout

## Endpoint

```http
POST /users/logout/
```

## Headers

```text
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token
```

## Request Body

```json
{
  "refresh_token": "your_refresh_token"
}
```

---

# API Endpoints

## Listings

| Method | Endpoint |
|---|---|
| GET | /listings/ |
| POST | /listings/ |
| GET | /listings/{id}/ |
| PUT | /listings/{id}/ |
| PATCH | /listings/{id}/ |
| DELETE | /listings/{id}/ |

---

## Properties

| Method | Endpoint |
|---|---|
| GET | /properties/properties/ |
| POST | /properties/properties/ |
| GET | /properties/properties/{id}/ |
| PUT | /properties/properties/{id}/ |
| PATCH | /properties/properties/{id}/ |
| DELETE | /properties/properties/{id}/ |

---

## Transactions

| Method | Endpoint |
|---|---|
| GET | /transactions/transactions/ |
| POST | /transactions/transactions/ |
| GET | /transactions/transactions/{id}/ |

---

# API Documentation



http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/doc/
```



